def calculate_objective(assignments: DSList(length=6, elem_type=DSInt())) -> int:
    max_box = 0
    for i in range(1, N_ITEMS + 1):
        box_nr = assignments[i]
        if box_nr > max_box:
            max_box = box_nr
    return max_box
